            "heading": "The billing lifecycle end to end",
            "text": "The **billing lifecycle** runs from quote and contract, to invoicing, to payment collection, to handling failures, disputes, and refunds, and finally to reconciliation and reporting. Money can leak at every stage: a mispriced quote, a wrong invoice, a failed card, a chargeback, or an over-generous refund.\n\nAs Director you don't process the invoices yourself, but you own the design of this lifecycle across your **Sr. Billing Specialist** and the Manila billing and collections team. Knowing where each dollar can slip out lets you point your team at the highest-leverage leaks instead of firefighting whatever screams loudest."
