            "heading": "What autonomous engagement does",
            "text": "**Autonomous lead engagement** is the AI reaching out to a new or existing lead on its own — answering questions, qualifying interest, and keeping a conversation alive across text and email — without the agent lifting a finger. It is the feature customers picture when they say they bought 'the AI.'\n\nThe payoff is emotional as much as economic. Agents hate the grind of chasing cold leads and following up for weeks. When the AI carries that load, it removes the exact work that causes agents to let leads rot, which is why this feature anchors most ROI stories."
